{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_01","textHome":"我叫美凪纱纱罗。父亲是一名救援队员，是我@最尊敬的人。不管多么危险的境地，为了救人@都不会退缩的父亲，就像绘本里的骑士一样@帅气。拥有这样的父亲，作为他的女儿……@我也想要成为强大的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_18","textHome":"能实现孩童时候远大梦想的人，寥寥无几吧？@所以，能实现骑士梦的我也算是个幸运儿。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_19","textHome":"帮助他人的这条道路没有终点。@今后我也会不断前进……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_20","textHome":"能作为一个魔法少女而努力……@我想父亲也一定会为我感到高兴。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_21","textHome":"龙生龙凤生凤，救援队的女儿也是救援队！@嘿嘿，随便说说啦。我会继承父亲的意志……@认真地为帮助他人而努力！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_22","textHome":"父亲救人于危难，我救人逃离魔女的魔爪……@很开心我们都为了救助他人而倾注着力量。@当然……魔法少女的事，只能对父亲保密了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_23","textHome":"我能成为像父亲一样的人吗？以前，@我在电视上看到过父亲救援行动中的身姿。@正直勇敢，非常帅气……@我也想以那样的姿态，被大家看见。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_24","textHome":"我一直在等你一起训练！@那么，先从准备活动开始吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_25","textHome":"早上好！昨天睡得很香所以今天感觉很清爽！@我可不会因为是早上就拖拖拉拉的哦？@骑士可是24小时待命，全年无休的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_26","textHome":"糟糕！都这个时间了！午饭！该吃午饭了！@为了保证每时每刻都是准备万全的状态，@一定要按时摄取一日三餐！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_27","textHome":"今天社团活动结束后也去巡逻吧！@嘛，虽然很累……@但是为了守护城市的和平，就是举手之劳！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_03","textHome":"我终于成为了想要成为的自己……！@但……这种空虚的感觉是为何？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_28","textHome":"糟糕！都这个时间了！睡觉！该进被窝了！@睡眠不足导致反应迟钝的话，@就帮不了别人了吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_29","textHome":"我真的很尊敬，从事救援工作的父亲。@既强大又温柔……他就是我理想中的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_30","textHome":"好的！我们也该出去了！@就算没人喊我，巡逻也是不可少的！@因为，我是守护神滨的骑士！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_31","textHome":"骑士不仅是剑术，也需要强大的内心。@所以我不会被恐惧吓倒……！不管是@什么样的敌人……我都会毫不犹豫地面对它！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_32","textHome":"乱战，很好！借此机会发挥一下日常锻炼的@成果！我一定会成为比谁都要强的骑士！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_33","textHome":"在参观社团活动之前就悠闲地打羽毛球吧。@职业比赛真的很厉害。超光速！你有看过吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_34","textHome":"我加入了学校的羽毛球部。@要是有击剑部的话我就去击剑部了。@是的，因为我要以骑士的身份来锻炼自己。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_35","textHome":"我的父亲真的很帅气！诶？已经听够了吗？@不是不是！现在要说的是外表！@个子很高，身体也很结实……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_36","textHome":"我有那么性急吗？大家总是这么说我……@但是……但是哦？因为救人这种事攸关性命，@一定要抢时间哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_37","textHome":"从小憧憬的骑士绘本，我到现在都随身携带。@烦恼时翻开看看，就能获得不可思议的勇气。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_04","textHome":"我的目的是被人感谢吗……？是这样吗？@快回答呀……我……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300400}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_38","textHome":"仅仅满足于守护神滨的人不能称为骑士吧？@我呢，想一步一步成为守护世界和平的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":300400}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_39","textHome":"Ha…ve…you…finished……@嗯，诶？嗯……那个，你擅长英语吗？@请教一下我这里……我真的很不擅长英语……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_40","textHome":"边看电视边打电话？明日香可做不到这种事。@她除了战斗之外，做什么都是单线程。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_41","textHome":"我许愿想要获得像骑士一般拯救他人的力量，@然后成为了魔法少女。所以，成为魔法少女@这件事，就是我的愿望。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":1}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_42","textHome":"骑士要正面对决！岿然不动！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_43","textHome":"我会变得更强！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_44","textHome":"能保护大家真是太开心了……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_45","textHome":"要是父亲能看到就好了。"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_46","textHome":"这是骑士应尽的职责！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_63","textHome":"让你看看……什么是真正的强大……！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_05","textHome":"我想我们合作也不错嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_64","textHome":"知道吗？正义……必将得胜……！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_65","textHome":"我是不会允许……邪恶以胜利告终的……！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":400}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_66","textHome":"不取得和平……故事就不会结束……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":300400,"motion":200}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3004_00_02","textHome":"是你在寻求帮助吗？我是美凪纱纱罗。@我来了就没问题了。